"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-showbiz-tom-daley-im-a-celebrity-contestant-retirement-diving-paris-olympics-b1176219.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz  The Standard's journalism is supported by our readers.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.081552228134181e-35, \"text\": \"The Standard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evening_Standard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley's odds to take part in the next series of I am A Celebrity... Get Me Out Of Here have shot up after heconfirmed his retirement from divingafter competing at the 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.338471909576078e-47, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old athlete made his Olympics debut aged just 14 at the Beijing Games in 2008 and 16 years later has he won a silver medal at the\\u00a0Paris\\u00a0Games to add to his collection of three bronzes and one gold.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After confirming on Mondaythat he will be hanging up his speedos,entering the Australian jungle could be a next step.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999692049594734, \"rank\": 2.2319031483354902e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest odds from Ladbrokes certainly agree, placing him at\\u00a0just 3/1 to appear on the next series when it returns in November hosted by Ant and Dec.  A number of other former Olympians have given it a go over the years, including Sam Quek and Amir Khan.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Quek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.910467671857008e-19, \"text\": \"Amir Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley is also no stranger himself to reality TV after serving as a mentor on ITV show Splash from 2013-2014 where he attempted to teachcelebritieshow to dive.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"score\": 0.931842604174716, \"rank\": 0.037963543887348274, \"text\": \"ITV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing his decision to make Paris his last Olympics, Daley toldBritish Vogue: \\\"It feels very, very surreal.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982251211, \"rank\": 1.7746724183460779e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure and expectation.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done\\u2026 but when I walked out, and saw my husband [Dustin Lance Black] and kids [Robbie and Phoenix] and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am here, and no matter what happens in the competition itself, I am going to be happy.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2381, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9185892155531359, \"rank\": 0.08862539762574732, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", 